entry.value: SELECT "Post Code", "Primary Street Name", "Permission Status", "No of Bedrooms", "Unit Type", "Residential Development Type", "Building height (maximum storeys)", "Superseded date", "Started Date", "Completed date", Borough, SUBSTRING("Permission Date", 1, 2) || SUBSTRING("Permission Date", 4, 2) || SUBSTRING("Permission Date", 7, 4) AS DateOnly FROM FLOWFILE
SELECT RowID,"Superseded date", "Started Date","Completed date" FROM FLOWFILE
SELECT RowID, "Post Code", "Primary Street Name" FROM FLOWFILE
SELECT RowID, "Permission Status", "No of Bedrooms", "Unit Type", "Residential Development Type", "Building height (maximum storeys)" FROM FLOWFILE
SELECT *, DateOnly || '_' || Borough || '_' || ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY DateOnly ORDER BY DateOnly) AS RowID FROM FLOWFILE
SELECT RowID, Borough, County, District, Street, PostalCode FROM FLOWFILE
SELECT RowID, Price, Number, Appartment FROM FLOWFILE
SELECT *, DateOnly || '_' || City || '_' || ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY "DateOnly" ORDER BY "DateOnly") AS RowID FROM FLOWFILE
SELECT Price, City, Borough, County, District, Street, Number, Appartment, PostalCode, SUBSTRING("Date", 9, 2) || SUBSTRING("Date", 6, 2) || SUBSTRING("Date", 1, 4) AS DateOnly FROM FLOWFILE
